byline.contributor: Sharifullah Sahak contributed reporting from Kabul, and an Afghan employee of The New York Times from Kunduz.

snippet: NATO forces said Haji Mali Khan was a “revered elder” in the brutal Pakistan-based clan and an uncle of two of its top leaders.
lead_paragraph: NATO forces said Haji Mali Khan was a “revered elder” in the brutal Pakistan-based clan and an uncle of two of its top leaders.

headline.main: NATO Says It Caught a Haqqani Clan Leader
